cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "LLMVault: An OWASP LLM Top 10 Training Range"
message: "If you use LLMVault, please cite it and credit the author."
type: software
authors:
  - alias: CyberSunil
    name: CyberSunil
repository-code: "https://github.com/CyberSunil/LLMVault"
abstract: >-
  LLMVault is a deliberately-vulnerable, CTF-style web application for practising
  the OWASP Top 10 for LLM Applications (2025): 25 labs across core, advanced
  (multi-turn), and encrypted expert tiers, each pairing an attack with its defense.
keywords:
  - LLM security
  - OWASP
  - prompt injection
  - AI red teaming
  - security training
license: MIT
year: 2026
